title: Warcraft III + SNGen + NoCD Patch
description:
For those who cant use the recently uploaded expansion pack (the frozen throne) here  the whole game Warcraft III Reign of Chaos. Unzip, burn the CD-Image, install from the freshly toasted cd (dont mind the warning during opening them, the images are made with panther) use a serial from the generator when asked. For gameplay you will only need to mount the nocd-dmg.

Here its running on tiger on a G4. There where never problems with it. Its compatible with the recently uploaded TFT-Expansion-Pack. I&#039;ve tested it.

Enjoy!
